# UI / UX Design Specification (JSON)

## Purpose

Defines a **clean, modern, professional UI/UX layout** for the State-Aware Pentest Notebook.

This is a **design contract**, not tied to a specific framework (works for Tauri, Electron, Web, or TUI-with-GUI).

---

## Design Principles

* Minimalist, distraction-free
* Information-dense but readable
* Keyboard-first
* Dark-mode friendly (pentester default)
* Explicit separation of *Knowledge*, *Engagement*, and *Suggestions*

---

## Global UI Layout

```json
{
  "layout": "three-pane",
  "theme": "dark",
  "font": {
    "family": "Inter, JetBrains Mono",
    "sizes": {
      "title": "18px",
      "body": "14px",
      "code": "13px"
    }
  }
}
```

---

## Main Application Shell

```json
{
  "appShell": {
    "header": {
      "left": "appName",
      "center": "activeEngagement",
      "right": ["currentPhase", "syncStatus"]
    },
    "sidebar": {
      "sections": ["Engagements", "Knowledge Base", "Rules"],
      "collapsible": true
    },
    "content": "dynamic"
  }
}
```

---

## Engagement View

```json
{
  "engagementView": {
    "panes": {
      "left": "targetAndServices",
      "center": "findingsEditor",
      "right": "suggestionPanel"
    }
  }
}
```

