## Target & Services Panel (Left)

```json
{
  "targetPanel": {
    "components": [
      "targetList",
      "openPorts",
      "serviceMap"
    ],
    "interactions": {
      "addPort": "modal",
      "editService": "inline"
    }
  }
}
```

