## Suggestion Panel (Right)

```json
{
  "suggestionPanel": {
    "groupBy": "service",
    "item": {
      "title": "techniqueTitle",
      "owaspTag": true,
      "confidence": true,
      "actions": ["view", "copyCommand", "markAsTried"]
    }
  }
}
```

