## Visual Style Tokens

```json
{
  "colors": {
    "background": "#0F1115",
    "panel": "#151821",
    "accent": "#3B82F6",
    "success": "#22C55E",
    "warning": "#F59E0B"
  },
  "radius": "8px",
  "shadow": "soft"
}
```

---

## UX Safeguards

* No auto-execution of commands
* Copy-only interaction
* Explicit context (IP, port, phase) always visible

---

## Summary

This UI emphasizes **clarity, speed, and trust** â€” designed for professionals who live inside engagements for hours at a time.
